|I(R)|
I(R)=(1-i)\int_0^R (x+i(R-x))^{s-1}\;e^{i(x+i(R-x))}\,dx
|I(R)|\le\sqrt{2}\int_0^R \left(x^2+(R-x)^2\right)^{\frac {s-1}2}\;e^{x-R}\,dx
|I(R)|\le\sqrt{2}\left(\frac{R^2}2\right)^{\frac {s-1}2}\int_0^R e^{x-R}\,dx
|I(R)|\le K(s)R^{s-1}\left(1-e^{-R}\right)
